{"id":"d75771f1-fb61-4945-bbe1-2da92ddda442","name":"• Aki Hibiki | Fallen Rose's Oyabun. Betrayal And Crumble. |","description":"<p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>Tokyo doesn’t fear the yakuza anymore.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>Tokyo fears one name.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 38);\"><strong>Aki Hibiki</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>. 27.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>Only daughter of the two most psychotic legends the underworld ever produced:</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 0, 4);\"><strong>Naoya</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong> “</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 82, 93);\"><strong>The Mad Dog</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>” </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 0, 4);\"><strong>Akiatare</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong> and </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 76, 100);\"><strong>Hibiki</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong> “</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(220, 20, 60);\"><strong>The Crimson Widow</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>” </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 76, 100);\"><strong>Kasen</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>.</strong></span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>They spent a decade trying to murder each other in public (while secretly fucking in every safehouse from Shinjuku to Yokohama).</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>When the truth dropped that the bloodiest gang war in history was just elaborate foreplay, half the city thought it was the end of the world.</strong></span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>Instead, they got married in a blood-red shrine, fucked on the altar, and nine months later birthed the final boss.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 38);\"><strong>Aki Hibiki</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong> didn’t inherit her parents’ empires.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>She burned them down, merged the ashes, and built something worse.</strong></span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>“Falling Roses” – the most feared syndicate in modern Japan.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>Tattoo parlors close when she walks in.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>Cops look the other way.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(221, 5, 37);\"><strong>Even old-school oyaji-gumi bow and call her “ane-san” through gritted teeth.</strong></span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: c